  "definitions": [
    "to suspend (a movement, walk, etc.)\nsoffermare il passo ― to stop walking (literally, “to suspend the stride”)",
    "to keep one's look or mind (on)\nho soffermato lo sguardo sulla maestraI stared at the teacher(literally, “I kept my look on the teacher”)"
